Introduction

Huh Yunjin is a South Korean-American singer-songwriter, composer and dancer under Source Music. She is best known as the main vocalist of the girl group LE SSERAFIM.

In 2018, she appeared as a contestant on the survival show Produce 48 where she represented Pledis Entertainment. She was eliminated in episode 11 after ranking in 26th place.

Huh Yunjin debuted as a member of LE SSERAFIM on May 2, 2022, with their first mini album "FEARLESS".

On August 9, 2022, Yunjin released her first solo song titled "Raise y_our glass" to commemorate 100 days since LE SSERAFIM's debut.
